Dialogue: 8,1:57:03.25,1:57:04.00,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.83,1:57:14.67,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2\c&HFFFFFF&}Wow　果てなき空
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.67,1:57:21.97,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2\c&HFFFFFF&}Wow　星を目指せ
